ast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">”的小客车车道通行；持有《货运汽车城区道路行驶证》并悬挂大型汽车号牌的车辆在三环路辅道通行时，可借用三环路立交桥桥面进行交通转换，但桥面通行范围仅限于桥前桥后最近的进出口之间路段。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">．遇大型活动、城市道路建设及其它情况需调整交通组织措施时，特许经营权受让方必须服从公安机关发布的相关通告规定和执勤民警的指挥，由此而引起的特许经营权（货运汽车城区道路使用权）不能行使的损失由特许经营权受让方承担。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">．对持有《货运汽车城区道路行驶证》并被认定为成都市城市共同配送试点车辆的，在临时停车上下货物和高峰期行驶时段上另作规定。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　六、各类证受理地点：成都市公安局交通管理局一分局至六分局、各区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">县交警大队（交警七分局除外）；外籍</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">黑底牌照</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">的货运汽车在交警五分局申办。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　七、工作流程</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（一）资格确认和竞价日期为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-famil