ont-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">，在成都市公共资源交易服务中心开标产生竞价结果，并在各受理点公布。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（三）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日，竞得人到原受理点签订《特许经营合同》、交款（现金或刷卡均可）及领取《货运汽车城区道路行驶证》，每天的工作时间为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9:00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11:30,13:00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16:00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　八、各类证受理所需手续及相关规定</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（一）竞价定车定号证须出示《机动车行驶证》原件提交复印件、竞价报名单，私车须出示车主身份证原件提交复印件、竞价报名单，如需要委托代理的，除携带上述证照外，还须携带委托代理人身份证原件提交复印件，以及授权委托书原件。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（二）申办</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">H</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证的限已交纳“五路一桥”通行费的各类货运汽车，车主须出示《机动车行驶证》、交纳“五路一桥”通行费的发票，在交警部门免费办理。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　九、根据《中华人民共和国拍卖法》的有关规定，本公司将按成交价格的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4%(</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">百分之四</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">向买受人收取佣金。本公司将出具佣金收款收据，如需换取佣金发票，请于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日起到本公司办理。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　十、竞价人完成竞价后，现场打印的竞价凭证经竞价人当场核对无误后执有。竞价结果一经公布，竞得人须持申办时提交的手续到原受理点签订《特许经营合同》，交纳竞得价款和佣金（现金或刷卡均可）后方可领取《货运汽车城区道路行驶证》。支票须提前下账（以确认到账为准</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">转账务必载名款项用途“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2017</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年入城证竞价成交价款”，否则，由此导致的不利后果自行负担）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">价款户名：成都市财政局应缴预算归集户，开户行：工行成都高新支行民丰大道分理处，账号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4402235009008901287</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">；佣金户名：四川省嘉诚拍卖有限公司</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span \"mso-spacerun: yes\"> </span></span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">开户行：工行成都高新支行民丰大道分理处，账号：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4402235319000013791</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span \"mso-spacerun: yes\"> </span></span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　十一、本次“货运汽车城区道路使用权”公开竞价工作由四川省成都市蜀都公证处进行公证。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　咨询电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">028-86645568</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　监督电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">028-86276656</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　公司地址：成都市青羊区东城根上街</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">78</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号建设大厦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">楼</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">\n   <o:p>\n    <span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"></span></span>\n   </o:p></span></span></p> \n<span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"></p> </span></span>\n<span \"font-size: 18px\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"text-indent: 273pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 26.0\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"> 四川省嘉诚拍卖有限公司</span></span></span></p> </span> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"text-indent: 288.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 27.5\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 2016</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日</span></span></span></span></p>', '1100021278', '成都市交通管理局', '2016-11-22 18:03:33');
INSERT INTO `g2monitor_news` VALUES ('90D70EC843DB4E129C74EDA8BF2E7887', '关于2017年度货运汽车城区道路行驶证管理的通告', '2016-10-20 09:35:30', '7199', '1', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　为缓解城区道路交通拥堵，科学合理调控城区道路交通流量，依照《中华人民共和国道路交通安全法》等法律、法规，现就取得</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2017</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年度《货运汽车城区道路行驶证》车辆通行的有关事项通告如下：</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　一、《货运汽车城区道路行驶证》的分类</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　定车定号证：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A1</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A2</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B1</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B2</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">C1</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">C2</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">D</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">H</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　二、车型及载质量使用规定</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（一）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A1</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B1</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">C1</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证：限悬挂小型汽车号牌（蓝色）的货运汽车使用。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（二）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A2</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B2</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">C2</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证：限悬挂大型汽车号牌（黄色）且核定载质量</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">吨（含）以内的货运汽车使用。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（三）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">D</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证：限水泥砼罐车使用。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（四）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">H</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证：限已交纳“五路一桥”通行费的各类货运汽车使用（从事建筑垃圾运输车、危化品运输车、新能源货车除外）。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　三、各类证使用规定</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（一）允许持</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A1</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">A2</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">证的货运汽车每日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7:00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22:00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">在三环路（含）以内、南部新区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">三环路（含）以南、剑南大道（含）以东、天府二街（含）、世纪城路（含）、世纪城东路（含）一线以北、科华南路（含）一线以西区域，（以下简称“南部新区”）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、天府大道（天府二街至麓山大道）、熊猫大道（将军碑路至蜀龙大道）、东林二路（三环路至熊猫大道）的城区道路行驶（在上述区域行驶须按照交通标志、标线的具体指示行驶），但禁止工作日的早、晚高峰时段</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(7:00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9:00,17:00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20:00)</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">以及国家法定假日的晚高峰时段（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17:00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20:00</span><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">），在上述城区道路行驶。</span></span></span></span></p> \n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" \"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span \"line-height: 36px\"><span \"font-size: 18px\"><span \"font-family: 宋体\"><span \"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　（二）允许持</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B1</span><spa